1. To create scheduel:
	POST: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schedule/
2. To get schedule list:
	GET: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schedule/
3. To retrieve schedule:
	GET: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schedule/<schedule_id>/
4. To update schedule:
	PATCH: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schedule/<schedule_id>/
5. To accept schedule:
	PATCH: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schedule/<schedule_id>/accept/
6. To cancel schedule:
	PATCH: http://127.0.0.1:8000/schedule/<schedule_id>/cancel/
